{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840737703,"sessionID":"ses_287a5a358ffeTRbhh1WPFMz6t3","part":{"id":"prt_d785b3987001q3oC0au8p1bn0n","messageID":"msg_d785b1b40001cgiITeAOekTMBC","sessionID":"ses_287a5a358ffeTRbhh1WPFMz6t3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-20e4b0d40c374e5abe54890e5609b167","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/tasks-AR-002.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/tasks-AR-002.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 Task Checklist: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Status\n4: Stage: ST-3 (Design) - Completed\n5: Phase: ST-4 (Implementation) - In Progress\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Phase 1: Type Definition (CodeInterpreter)\n10: ### [ ] TASK-001: Define CodeInterpreterSpec\n11: **Description**: Create `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct with image, runtime, timeout, resources, env, and enabledPackages fields.\n12: \n13: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n14: \n15: **Requirements**:\n16: - `Image string` - required field, container image for interpreter\n17: - `Runtime string` - optional field with default \"python\" and enum validation (python;javascript;typescript;go)\n18: - `Timeout *metav1.Duration` - optional field with default \"5m\" and duration format validation\n19: - `Resources *SandboxContainerResources` - optional field, reuses existing type\n20: - `Env []SandboxEnvVar` - optional field, reuses existing type\n21: - `EnabledPackages []string` - optional field, specifies allowed packages\n22: - Default value markers: `+kubebuilder:default=\"python\"` for Runtime, `+kubebuilder:default=\"5m\"` for Timeout\n23: - Enum validation marker for Runtime: `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=python;javascript;typescript;go`\n24: - Duration format validation marker for Timeout: `+kubebuilder:validation:Format=duration`\n25: \n26: **Verification**:\n27: ```bash\n28: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreterSpec\n29: ```\n30: \n31: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n32: - `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct compiles without errors\n33: - `Image` field is required\n34: - `Runtime` field has enum validation and default value markers\n35: - `Timeout` field has duration format validation and default value markers\n36: - `Resources` and `Env` reference existing Sandbox types correctly\n37: - JSON tags use camelCase with `omitempty` for optional fields\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ### [ ] TASK-002: Define CodeInterpreterStatus\n42: **Description**: Create `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct with ready, conditions, and observedGeneration fields.\n43: \n44: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n45: \n46: **Requirements**:\n47: - `Ready bool` - optional field, indicates whether interpreter is ready\n48: - `Conditions []metav1.Condition` - optional field, latest observations of state\n49: - `ObservedGeneration int64` - optional field, most recent generation observed by controller\n50: - Follows Kubernetes status conventions\n51: \n52: **Verification**:\n53: ```bash\n54: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreterStatus\n55: ```\n56: \n57: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n58: - `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct compiles without errors\n59: - `Conditions` field uses standard Kubernetes `metav1.Condition` type\n60: - JSON tags use camelCase with `omitempty` for optional fields\n61: - Status fields are optional as per Kubernetes conventions\n62: \n63: ---\n64: \n65: ### [ ] TASK-003: Define CodeInterpreter main type\n66: **Description**: Create `CodeInterpreter` struct with TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, and Status.\n67: \n68: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n69: \n70: **Requirements**:\n71: - Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n72: - Contains `Spec CodeInterpreterSpec` and `Status CodeInterpreterStatus`\n73: - Kubebuilder markers:\n74:   - `+genclient`\n75:   - `+genclient:nonNamespaced` (if non-namespaced, remove if namespaced is intended)\n76:   - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n77:   - `+k8s:openapi-gen=true`\n78:   - `+kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci;codeinterpreter`\n79:   - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n80:   - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Ready\",type=\"boolean\",JSONPath=\".status.ready\"`\n81:   - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Runtime\",type=\"string\",JSONPath=\".spec.runtime\"`\n82:   - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n83: \n84: **Verification**:\n85: ```bash\n86: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreter\n87: ```\n88: \n89: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n90: - `CodeInterpreter` struct compiles without errors\n91: - All kubebuilder markers are present and correct\n92: - ShortNames \"ci\" and \"codeinterpreter\" are configured\n93: - Print columns for Ready, Runtime, and Age are configured\n94: - Status subresource is enabled\n95: \n96: ---\n97: \n98: ### [ ] TASK-004: Define CodeInterpreterList type\n99: **Description**: Create `CodeInterpreterList` struct for collection operations.\n100: \n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 761. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 Task Checklist: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Status\nStage: ST-3 (Design) - Completed\nPhase: ST-4 (Implementation) - In Progress\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Type Definition (CodeInterpreter)\n### [ ] TASK-001: Define CodeInterpreterSpec\n**Description**: Create `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct with image, runtime, timeout, resources, env, and enabledPackages fields.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- `Image string` - required field, container image for interpreter\n- `Runtime string` - optional field with default \"python\" and enum validation (python;javascript;typescript;go)\n- `Timeout *metav1.Duration` - optional field with default \"5m\" and duration format validation\n- `Resources *SandboxContainerResources` - optional field, reuses existing type\n- `Env []SandboxEnvVar` - optional field, reuses existing type","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/tasks-AR-002.md","time":{"start":1775840737695,"end":1775840737701}}}}
