ources struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go\n136: grep -q \"type SandboxEnvVar struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go\n137: ```\n138: \n139: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n140: - All shared Sandbox types exist and compile\n141: - Types have the correct field definitions\n142: - Types have proper JSON tags\n143: \n144: ---\n145: \n146: ## Phase 2: Scheme Registration\n147: ### [ ] TASK-006: Register CodeInterpreter types in scheme\n148: **Description**: Update `register.go` to register CodeInterpreter and CodeInterpreterList in the scheme.\n149: \n150: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n151: \n152: **Requirements**:\n153: - Add `&CodeInterpreter{}` to `addKnownTypes()` function\n154: - Add `&CodeInterpreterList{}` to `addKnownTypes()` function\n155: - Types are registered with correct GroupVersion (runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1)\n156: \n157: **Verification**:\n158: ```bash\n159: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreterRegistration\n160: ```\n161: \n162: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n163: - `CodeInterpreter` is registered in scheme\n164: - `CodeInterpreterList` is registered in scheme\n165: - `addKnownTypes()` function compiles without errors\n166: - Scheme can create CodeInterpreter objects via New() method\n167: \n168: ---\n169: \n170: ### [ ] TASK-007: Verify SchemeGroupVersion is correct\n171: **Description**: Verify that SchemeGroupVersion constant matches the API group for CodeInterpreter.\n172: \n173: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n174: \n175: **Requirements**:\n176: - `SchemeGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n177: - Matches CodeInterpreter API group\n178: \n179: **Verification**:\n180: ```bash\n181: grep -q 'SchemeGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}' pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go\n182: ```\n183: \n184: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n1