fic tests: TypeMeta, SpecDefaults, Status, List, Resources, EnvVar, RuntimeEnum, EnabledPackages, DeepCopy (6 tests)\n\n### ⚠️ **Missing Implementation: client-go Library Generation**\n\n**Spec Requirement**: The spec references client-go library generation with module path `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n\n**Current Status**: client-go code has NOT been generated\n\n**What's Missing**:\n- ❌ `client-go/` directory does not exist\n- ❌ Clientset (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n- ❌ Typed clients for CodeInterpreter (`clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`)\n- ❌ Informer factory and informers for CodeInterpreter\n- ❌ Listers for CodeInterpreter\n- ❌ Fake clients for testing\n\n**Required for client-go generation**:\n- Run `make gen-client` or equivalent code generation script using `k8s.io/code-generator`\n- Need codegen configuration (e.g., `hack/update-codegen.sh` or Makefile targets)\n\n### 📊 **Summary**\n\n| Component | Status | File Location |\n|-----------|--------|---------------|\n| CodeInterpreter type definition | ✅ Complete | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go:742-806` |\n| Scheme registration | ✅ Complete | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go:43-48` |\n| DeepCopy methods | ✅ Complete | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go:1061-1171` |\n| Unit tests | ✅ Complete | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go` |\n| client-go library | ❌ Missing | N/A |\n\n### ✅ **Tests Passing**\n\n```\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 -v\n=== RUN   TestCodeInterpreterTypeMeta\n--- PASS: TestCodeInterpreterTypeMeta (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestCodeInterpreterSpecDefaults\n--- PASS: TestCodeInterpreterSpecDefaults (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestCodeInterpreterStatus\n--- PASS: TestCodeInterpreterStatus (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestCodeInterpreterList\n--- PASS: TestCodeInterpreterList (0.00s)\n... (24 CodeInterpreter tests passing)\nPASS\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1        (cached)\n```\n\n### 📝 **Recommendations